## DESIGN SYSTEM RULES (apply to ALL new/rewritten pages)

```
Fonts:       font-heading, font-body, font-ui
Colors:      bg-background, text-foreground, border-foreground/10
Opacity:     text-foreground/70 for secondary text, /20 for dividers
Hover:       hover:opacity-70 or hover:border-foreground/30
Transitions: transition-opacity or transition-all
Buttons:     bg-foreground text-background px-8 py-4 font-ui text-sm uppercase tracking-wider
Links:       font-ui text-sm uppercase tracking-wide underline hover:no-underline
Spacing:     py-20 sections, max-w-6xl or max-w-4xl mx-auto, px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12
```

Never use raw Tailwind color classes like `text-gray-800`, `bg-white`, `text-blue-600`. Always use design token classes above.

